window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A man out of time. A woman bound by duty. A love that defies the centuries.</p> <p>Gabe Thorne has always been fascinated by history, but he never expected to live it. When a visit to the past turns into something more, he finds himself drawn to Maggie Murphy, a fiercely independent innkeeper with a sharp wit and a guarded heart. But when circumstances pull Maggie into Gabe’s modern world, she faces an impossible choice—embrace a future she never imagined or return to the life she’s always known.</p> <p>As past and present collide, Gabe and Maggie must navigate a love complicated by time itself. Can Maggie truly find happiness in a world so different from her own, or will love prove timeless enough to overcome the greatest divide?</p> <p>If you adore heartfelt time-travel romance with captivating characters, emotional depth, and a touch of humor, <i>Destined Across Time</i> will sweep you away on an unforgettable journey.</p> <p>Start listening today and fall in love across the ages.</p>"; 
